snippet.title: Arcade Game: Tube Panic (1984 Nichibutsu / Fujitek)
snippet.description:
A shooting 'em up game where you pilot your ship through 3D view of vast zones and large tubular vortex levels full of enemies. The vast zones has similar gameplay to Tempest, Blaster (1983), and Gyruss. After completing the tubular levels,  you must dock with the mothership. 

Gameplay starts at 4:41

Note: Used invincibility cheat after down to last life.
